strings: <se_high>*: I couldn't sleep after seeing this...
<se_high>*: I mean, no one expected the Joker to cross an ocean like that!
<se_high>*: As it flows along the coast, it inevitably leads to baccarat.
<se_high>*: I want to erase this image from my head. Maybe ghosts or something...
<se_low>King of tricks: <hero>Did you hear that?! Apparently she was referring to Dormago!
<se_low>King of tricks: You have to look inside the slot machine to see if you can smell it.
